title: Person of Interest - Welcome back Finch (05x12)
author: POI - Best Of
comment: That moment when the door opens and Finch is standing there. Brilliant!
1:03-1:05 - Two brief seconds where you contemplate whether Finch killed someone or not.

F: Good bye, John.
(Sameen: And what about me?)
The doors opening and Finch standing there might be my favourite moment of the series.
I know the first time they fought John was wounded, but that's the second time that operative owned him.
